keyMappings:
unmap h
unmap n
unmap e
unmap i
map e scrollUp
map n scrollDown
map h scrollLeft
map i scrollRight
map E scrollPageUp
map N scrollPageDown
map R reload hard
map g^ firstTab
map <a-H> firstTabchrome-extension://dbepggeogbaibhgnhhndojpepiihcmeb/pages/options.html#
map <a-I> lastTab
map <C-N> scrollFullPageDown
map <C-E> scrollFullPageUp
map yl LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl
# Search through your opened tabs
map t Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map T createTab https://www.google.com/
# Open multiple links in new tabs
map gl LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
unmap >>
unmap <<
map < moveTabLeft
map > moveTabRight
unmap d
map dd removeTab
map <C-r> restoreTab
map l goBack
map L goForward
" Open a Link in current tab using a new tab
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map H previousTab
map I nextTab
map k performFind
map K performBackwardsFind
